{
  "stem": "17135.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if you needed somebody, that-- an important person that want to save, you could somehow, through proteksia, arrange, that he was sent to a working kommando where the chances of chicanery and of murder was the least.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Least.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, every day was a fight for survival.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and I'll give an example.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If he came home from work, then sometimes those bullies, I call them, the SS bullies, came and said, oh, you ate, now let's do some sport.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Within the barracks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was-- I was so small-- the barracks were-- were built on a-- how do you call it-- about, I would say, this high.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- I was small enough to crawl under the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They couldn't see me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That-- that way I saved myself not being beaten.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was absolutely murderous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They didn't gas the people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Through chicanery, beating, and lack of medical treatment and lack of food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I give an example.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was so bad with the abscesses-- they were full of abscess-- that the SS agreed because the stink was so-- that the people couldn't stand it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was, in-- in between the two wings, there was a latrine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They put the people in the latrine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were lying on the floor and dying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Literally dying.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And at night, people had to go to relieve themself, they're stepping on them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I mean, it-- it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In other words, there was no human-- they're totally dehumanized us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They totally-- they did everything to take away any sense of humanity from us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll give an example.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somehow, these-- those theories, those political theories, that they tried to-- to-- to lecture us.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
